name: Apocalypsis Flos
description:
Apocalypsis Flos is part of the Meta Filipina collection, in collaboration with ohhhhhhhmae, who is a music and pixel artists. 

This is the story of a struggling young Filipina navigating through the Xperia Ed of the pandemic. In a apocalyptic time, the key is to continue to find beauty . With the combination with my love of color and flowers and my sisters love for retro vibes. 

My mission in my pieces is to not only find an innocent presentation of creating, but to continue “finding beauty”.
